                    ### [Custom Potions](id:potions)
                    Custom effects can be added to a potion item with the `potions` attribute. Multiple effects are separated with a semicolon `;`. The format for custom potion item effects is: `potion_name:duration:potency:ambient`. The potion item's damage value will define the potion color and if it's a splash or normal potion.

                    The item's damage specifies the potion type. [Minecraft wiki - Potions](http://www.minecraftwiki.net/wiki/Potions).


